## Common Pitfalls

1. ‚ùå **DON'T** calculate Z-scores from raw values (use POINTS)
2. ‚ùå **DON'T** forget qualitative text ‚Üí points conversion
3. ‚ùå **DON'T** store only one composite score per fund (need 4, one per risk profile)
4. ‚ùå **DON'T** use the same ranking for all risk profiles
5. ‚ùå **DON'T** calculate Z-scores separately for each risk profile (they're universal)

